INSERT INTO `categories` VALUES (1,'Soap Flower','Delicately crafted from soap, these flowers look just like real blooms—but they never wilt. Soap flowers are perfect for decoration, gifts, or relaxing baths. Each petal is infused with a gentle fragrance, adding a touch of elegance and freshness to any space. Ideal for birthdays, anniversaries, or simply to show someone you care.','1753128081.jpg','2025-07-21 12:45:20','2025-08-21 02:05:48'),(2,'Fresh Flower','Freshly picked and beautifully arranged, our fresh flowers bring natural beauty and vibrant color to every moment. Each bouquet is carefully selected to ensure long-lasting freshness and fragrance. Perfect for birthdays, weddings, congratulations, or simply brightening someone\'s day with a heartfelt gesture.','1753128087.jpg','2025-07-21 12:48:47','2025-08-21 02:05:55'),(3,'Special Flower','Uniquely designed for unforgettable moments, our special flowers are crafted from creative materials like candy, money, or themed decorations. These one-of-a-kind arrangements are perfect for birthdays, graduations, or special celebrations where you want to surprise and delight. Each bouquet is not only eye-catching but also full of meaning and personal touch.','1753128094.jpg','2025-07-21 12:50:48','2025-08-21 02:06:03'),(4,'Souvenir','Souvenir\r\nThoughtfully selected to capture memories and emotions, our souvenirs are perfect for marking meaningful moments. From charming keepsakes to handcrafted gifts, each item carries a story—ideal for birthdays, anniversaries, travel memories, or simply showing appreciation. Small in size, big in sentiment.','1753128146.jpg','2025-07-21 13:02:26','2025-08-20 08:43:15');
